### Scheduler 定时任务 API 测试

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/scheduler
@token = your_token_here

### 1. 列出所有定时任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 获取任务状态 - example_every_minute
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_minute
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 获取任务状态 - example_daily_2am
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_daily_2am
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 获取任务状态 - example_every_5min
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_5min
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 禁用任务 - example_every_minute
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_minute/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 启用任务 - example_every_5min
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_5min/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 删除任务 - example_every_5min
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/example_every_5min
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 再次列出所有任务（验证删除）
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
